title: Internationals storm back into Presidents Cup
text: Oct. 10, 2015 | 12:06 AM Internationals storm back into Presidents Cup Bae Sang-Moon of South Korea (L) and Danny Lee of New Zealand (R) celebrate their win on the 18th hole during the second round four-ball matches at the 2015 Presidents Cup at the Jack Nicklaus Golf Club in Incheon, west of Seoul, on October 9, 2015. AFP PHOTO / JUNG YEON-JE Share Reuters     10, 2015, on page 13. Recommended
